\|A\|\leq\|\varphi\|
 |\langle Ax,y\rangle|=\left|\sum_{s,t}x_s\bar{y_t}\langle Ae_s,e_t\rangle \right| =\left|\sum_{s,t}x_s\bar{y_t}\,\varphi(E_{st}) \right| =\left|\varphi\left(\sum_{s,t}x_s\bar{y_t}\,E_{st}\right) \right|\\ \leq\|\varphi\|\,\left\|\sum_{s,t}x_s\bar{y_t} E_{st} \right\| =\|\varphi\|\,\left\|\sum_{s}x_sE_{s1}\,\left(\sum_t{y_t} E_{t1}\right)^* \right\|\\ \leq\|\varphi\|\,\left\|\sum_{s}x_sE_{s1}\right\|\,\left\|\sum_t{y_t} E_{t1} \right\| =\|\varphi\|\,\|x\|\,\|y\|. 
